The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, social-worker
3 different games are played: go, bridge, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the project-manager is between the engineer and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person playing bridge is the social-worker##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Hobby       | drawing       | traveling       | chess    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager | engineer |
| Game       | bridge      | canasta         | go |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

