2. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the nurse is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
