.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
3 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, dog
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person drinking water is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water          | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Pet           | hedgehog | dog | frog         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

