3. the fan of disco is between the futuristic house and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the fan of reggae is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the gothic-revival house and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| House      | futuristic | wooden     | gothic-revival        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Pet           | rat           | goldfish    | mouse       |

