.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, iced-tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the car##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the car##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person driving the tram and the person drinking mirinda##2
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Beverage       | mirinda | iced-tea   | cola   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 